data.description: Truly unique home on rare oversized corner lot, backing to greenbelt, in coveted Stonebridge Ranch community! Custom designer choices throughout make it stand out. The grand entrance leads you to a beautiful dining room with Venetian plaster ceilings & butler's pantry. Entertain guests in the gourmet kitchen with large island & impressive brick stove surround. Study features a wall to wall built in & plantation shutters. Upstairs you will find 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, a large game room with cozy built in lounger & a media room with pillar accents. Fine details throughout like archway surrounds combined with McKinney ISD and Stonebridge Ranch Amenities, this home has it all!
